      Simple but good

      Bake and brew is a staple of life in Old Airport. We drop in here occasionally to get breakfast or brunch. They do a range of waffles, breakfast foods and a good coffee within a decent place to sit and relax. Like many places here you need to be pro-active in getting the attention of the waiter when you are ready and they cook to order so it’s not quick but that’s how brunch should be.

      Precious_i61

      Great vibes and veggie friendly ;)

      Cosy coffeehouse nestled in the hustle and bustle of Addis.

      Perfect for a quick coffee catch up with friends - or if you have time, the extensive menu also allows for a more informal dining experience.

      The homemade lentil soup and selection of fresh salads were both winners...not forgetting to mention the mini bakery at the front which served up the most indulgent chocolate cake!

      Staff are friendly and attentive, making it a really pleasant environment. Definitely will be coming back on my next trip and would highly recommend!
